00:17:29.859 --> 00:17:33.859
the western part of the United States year after year.

00:17:33.859 --> 00:17:40.579
Those problems can threaten our zeal and enthusiasm.

00:17:40.579 --> 00:17:42.579
So what can we do?

00:17:42.579 --> 00:17:44.579
Well, there's an English expression

00:17:44.579 --> 00:17:46.579
that originates with firefighters.

00:17:46.579 --> 00:17:51.579
The expression is to fight fire with fire.

00:17:51.579 --> 00:17:53.579
