00:17:57.579 --> 00:18:01.579
That controlled fire consumes combustible materials.

00:18:01.579 --> 00:18:04.579
So when the wildfire advances to that point,

00:18:04.579 --> 00:18:06.579
there's no fuel left,

00:18:06.579 --> 00:18:08.579
and the wildfire goes out.

00:18:09.579 --> 00:18:11.579
Fight fire with fire.

00:18:11.579 --> 00:18:15.579
Keep your zeal for the ministry burning brightly.

