00:57:17.030 --> 00:57:22.030
are vital links in the chain leading to a Bible study.

00:57:22.030 --> 00:57:26.210
In our ministry,

00:57:26.210 --> 00:57:28.210
we often compliment the householder

00:57:28.210 --> 00:57:31.210
for the beautiful flowers or our plants in their yard,

00:57:31.210 --> 00:57:35.210
just like the sister did in the video.

00:57:35.210 --> 00:57:38.210
But how do they get that way?

00:57:38.210 --> 00:57:42.210
Well, the householder probably watered them on set days

00:57:42.210 --> 00:57:46.210
or even used an automatic sprinkler timer

00:57:46.210 --> 00:57:49.210
to schedule regular watering cycles.

00:57:49.210 --> 00:57:53.210
You need to have healthy and vibrant plants.

00:57:53.210 --> 00:57:57.210
Watering cannot be left to chance.

00:57:57.210 --> 00:58:00.210
Well, how can we apply that to our ministry?

00:58:01.210 --> 00:58:05.210
Before leaving a person that has shown interest,

00:58:05.210 --> 00:58:10.210
endeavor to set the proper time to water.

00:58:10.210 --> 00:58:13.210
The water of truth will come on.

00:58:13.210 --> 00:58:16.210
See, perhaps a wed day or hour

00:58:16.210 --> 00:58:19.210
would you like for me to return to continue our discussion

00:58:19.210 --> 00:58:21.210
or to answer the question.

00:58:21.210 --> 00:58:26.210
This consideration really dignifies the person,

00:58:26.210 --> 00:58:30.210
allowing them to share in setting the appointment.

00:58:30.210 --> 00:58:33.210
It's important that we be willing to water

00:58:33.210 --> 00:58:39.210
an interested person at the most convenient time for them.

00:58:39.210 --> 00:58:42.210
Then, just like setting a timer,

00:58:42.210 --> 00:58:45.210
put that appointment where you'll remember it.

00:58:45.210 --> 00:58:49.210
The sister in the video put it in her electronic calendar

00:58:49.210 --> 00:58:53.969
so she could be reminded later.

00:58:53.969 --> 00:58:56.969
If you promise someone that you'll return

00:58:56.969 --> 00:58:58.969
then keep your promise.

00:58:58.969 --> 00:59:00.969
Remember Jesus' simple statement

00:59:00.969 --> 00:59:03.969
recorded at Matthew 537,

00:59:03.969 --> 00:59:07.969
just like your word, yes, mean, yes?

00:59:07.969 --> 00:59:10.969
If they're truly interested,

00:59:10.969 --> 00:59:14.969
they may go to great efforts to keep the appointment.

00:59:14.969 --> 00:59:18.969
How disappointed they would be if we didn't show up.

00:59:18.969 --> 00:59:23.969
Following through is just too important

00:59:23.969 --> 00:59:26.969
to leave to chance.

00:59:26.969 --> 00:59:30.969
Because of the busy lives that people have today,

00:59:30.969 --> 00:59:34.969
