00:59:34.969 --> 00:59:37.969
even if you set an appointment.

00:59:37.969 --> 00:59:42.969
It's a good idea to try and obtain his contact information,

00:59:42.969 --> 00:59:45.969
maybe his phone number.

00:59:45.969 --> 00:59:48.969
Some publishers anticipate this challenge

00:59:48.969 --> 00:59:50.969
and simply ask,

00:59:50.969 --> 00:59:52.969
do you text?

00:59:52.969 --> 00:59:54.969
By simply texting,

00:59:54.969 --> 00:59:56.969
you may be able to keep in touch

00:59:56.969 --> 01:00:02.139
and cultivate the interest further.

01:00:02.139 --> 01:00:05.139
If you can't get his contact information

01:00:05.139 --> 01:00:09.139
and the person isn't home at the agreed upon time,

01:00:09.139 --> 01:00:11.139
you might leave a brief note

01:00:11.139 --> 01:00:14.139
just as the sister did in the video.

01:00:14.139 --> 01:00:16.139
This will assure the householder

01:00:16.139 --> 01:00:20.139
that you haven't forgotten them.

