01:01:33.690 --> 01:01:36.690
from many others that they may have.

01:01:36.690 --> 01:01:38.690
Do they have neighbors, friends,

01:01:38.690 --> 01:01:42.690
workmates or relatives that check in on them?

01:01:42.690 --> 01:01:46.690
But for them to grow spiritually,

01:01:46.690 --> 01:01:51.690
the water of truth from God's word must be dispensed.

01:01:51.690 --> 01:01:55.690
To convey just a brief scriptural thought

01:01:55.690 --> 01:02:03.579
may provide just enough to keep their spiritual soil moist.

01:02:03.579 --> 01:02:06.579
The work involved in following up interest

01:02:06.579 --> 01:02:09.579
is a very important assignment

01:02:09.579 --> 01:02:12.579
that Jehovah has given to each of us.

