It has helped us to see

01:13:45.699 --> 01:13:49.699
how we can maintain our zeal for the preaching work.

01:13:49.699 --> 01:13:52.699
It has instructed us to prepare well

01:13:52.699 --> 01:13:55.699
to share the truth with others.

01:13:55.699 --> 01:13:58.699
It showed us how to take the initiative

01:13:58.699 --> 01:14:00.699
