01:26:55.840 --> 01:26:58.840
or if you want to be very good at playing a certain sport,

01:26:58.840 --> 01:27:02.840
no doubt you're going to have some aching muscles,

01:27:02.840 --> 01:27:06.840
and no doubt you're going to have some hurt pride along the way too.

01:27:06.840 --> 01:27:09.840
Maybe you won't be very good when you first start,

01:27:09.840 --> 01:27:11.840
but what do you do?

01:27:11.840 --> 01:27:13.840
If you want to become good,

01:27:13.840 --> 01:27:16.840
if you want to reach your goal, you can't give up.

01:27:16.840 --> 01:27:18.840
You have to keep trying.

01:27:18.840 --> 01:27:20.840
Well, the same could be said

01:27:20.840 --> 01:27:23.840
about reaching our spiritual goals.

01:27:23.840 --> 01:27:29.840
You see, James mentions that trials often reveal our weaknesses.

01:27:29.840 --> 01:27:34.840
Maybe it's some aspect of our personality that needs improvement,

01:27:34.840 --> 01:27:38.840
or maybe it's something in our relationship with Jehovah.

01:27:38.840 --> 01:27:40.840
Maybe we need greater faith.

01:27:40.840 --> 01:27:43.840
Maybe we need greater trust.

01:27:43.840 --> 01:27:47.840
If we endure even during periods of trial

01:27:47.840 --> 01:27:52.840
and we refuse to give up, we become stronger.

01:27:52.840 --> 01:27:55.840
We become stronger in our spirituality

01:27:55.840 --> 01:27:57.840
and our relationship with Jehovah,

01:27:57.840 --> 01:28:00.840
our love for him, our faith in him,

01:28:00.840 --> 01:28:04.840
our trust in him just continues to grow.

01:28:04.840 --> 01:28:06.840
As James says, there in verse four,

01:28:06.840 --> 01:28:10.840
we become complete or sound in all respects,

01:28:10.840 --> 01:28:13.840
not lacking in anything.

01:28:13.840 --> 01:28:16.840
So, when those trials come,

01:28:16.840 --> 01:28:18.840
and they will come,

01:28:18.840 --> 01:28:21.840
don't look for a quick way out.

01:28:21.840 --> 01:28:25.840
And doer, keep going, don't give up.

01:28:25.840 --> 01:28:27.840
Seek advice from brothers and sisters

01:28:27.840 --> 01:28:31.840
who have successfully coped with similar challenges.

01:28:31.840 --> 01:28:34.840
And you too will be successful.

