01:29:09.300 --> 01:29:12.300
The elder I talked to gave me advice not to be picky

01:29:12.300 --> 01:29:14.300
on what kind of job I would have.

01:29:14.300 --> 01:29:17.300
He reminded me of Matthew 633

01:29:17.300 --> 01:29:21.300
and told me not to be overly anxious.

01:29:21.300 --> 01:29:24.300
Because of our good communication within the family,

01:29:24.300 --> 01:29:27.300
we were able to find solutions.

01:29:27.300 --> 01:29:30.300
My other siblings realized that they also shared responsibility

01:29:30.300 --> 01:29:33.300
in providing for the needs of the family.

01:29:33.300 --> 01:29:35.300
After one year of pioneering,

01:29:35.300 --> 01:29:38.300
