01:30:04.840 --> 01:30:07.840
I was really anxious.

01:30:07.840 --> 01:30:11.840
I wanted to show my trust in Jehovah by pioneering

01:30:11.840 --> 01:30:13.840
and give him an opportunity to show me

01:30:13.840 --> 01:30:19.050
that I can be happy in his service.

01:30:19.050 --> 01:30:22.050
I tried to express my appreciation for my cousins

01:30:22.050 --> 01:30:24.050
by what I said and did,

01:30:24.050 --> 01:30:28.640
and showed them love.

01:30:28.640 --> 01:30:34.210
They realized that I have changed for the better.

01:30:34.210 --> 01:30:37.210
I show more concern for others now.

01:30:37.210 --> 01:30:41.210
