01:31:00.829 --> 01:31:03.829
So then I started to feel really homesick.

01:31:03.829 --> 01:31:06.829
But my brothers and sisters, I'd go to the Kingdom Hall,

01:31:06.829 --> 01:31:08.829
and they were able to cope with the challenges

01:31:08.829 --> 01:31:11.829
that they were facing because they had Jehovah in their life.

01:31:11.829 --> 01:31:14.829
So that, their example really helped me to see

01:31:14.829 --> 01:31:17.829
that my circumstances don't need to change

01:31:17.829 --> 01:31:20.829
from my attitude to change.

